  "text": "Novel findings from our study demonstrate that -and -MHC isoforms have divergent effects on how the N terminus of cTnT modulates cardiac contractile dynamics. Inferences made from our study also have significant relevance to cardiac health and disease; for example, alterations in MHC and cTnT are known to occur via changes in isoform expression or mutations [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
